Getting excited for the return of I'm A Celebrity...? Well we've got some BRILLIANT news for you!

This year we're bringing you even more fun from Camp, with the arrival of I'm A Celebrity…The Daily Drop, a brand-new companion show for I'm A Celebrity…Get Me Out Of Here! that will air exclusively on the ITV Hub.

Hosted by Vick Hope from a virtual studio, the show will give fans an extra opportunity to delve deeper into the action from Camp, hear lively opinions and debates and get all the latest gossip. Once the celebrities start to leave the castle they'll also join Vick on The Daily Drop to share their experiences of life in camp.

show.summary: Cheyenne has been out of jail for six months now, working as a cleaner on the ferries whilst dreaming about traveling to the Amazon. Lola is a beautiful Parisian woman, selfish and ruthless, who has just arrived in the north of France to move in with her lover. But when Cheyenne witnesses Lola killing her lover's wife, she knows she's going to be accused of the crime because of her criminal past.
